{"tid":1203831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊的責任","createTime":"2019-06-11T13:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:33:28.000Z","uid":258638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5444ce9789adad6e189c0d5e18b08dde8cf4c03d","tid":1203831,"uid":258638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:33:28.000Z","msg":"如果警察打市民，就告佢違反警隊條例，等佢革職！<br />\n<br />\n第232章 《警隊條例》<br />\n10.警隊的責任<br />\n警隊的職責是採取合法措施以 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(c)防止損害生命及損毀財產；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap232!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap232%21zh-Hant-HK&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=dd206476\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap232!zh-Hant-HK</a>"}]}